# ============================================
# NOTES:
# ============================================
# Files that SHOULD be committed:
# - requirements.txt
# - manage.py
# - All application .py files
# - Templates and static files
# - README.md
# - settings.py (without secrets)
# - urls.py
# - wsgi.py, asgi.py
# ============================================